To configure an account to tweet:
1. Register a twitter application at http://dev.twitter.com/apps/new
    Access type must be Read & Write; callback url should be "SITES_ABSOLUTE_PATH/auth/callback.php"
2. Update config.php with consumer key, consumer secret & oauth callback url.
3. Visit index.php, sign in with twitter. After auth-ing, you'll get oauth token & oauth token secret which has to be updated in config.php.
That's it! 